Symbol.Script_3D:
!! Dryer
pen gs_cont_pen
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end
addz storage_hgh
! --- start of modifying to Shaft
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
if gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 then resol 8 if gs_detlevel_3D_m=2 then resol 24
if bShowMEP then
if useSysMat then w_mat = sMat k_mat = sMat gs_con_mat = sMat matGlass = sMat matDoorFrame = sMat matControlPanel = sMat matControl = sMat endif
call "MEP_m_ConnectionsACL_4" parameters SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = gs_con_mat, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1 = ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1 = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1 = ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1 = ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 16 endif
! --- end of modifying to Shaft
material w_mat
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_resol=3
if gs_shadow=0 then SHADOW OFF
add a/2,b,0 hotspot -a/2,0,0-storage_hgh hotspot 0,0,ZZYZX-storage_hgh hotspot a/2,0,0-storage_hgh hotspot 0,-b/2,0-storage_hgh hotspot a/2,-b,0-storage_hgh hotspot -a/2,-b,0-storage_hgh
hotspot -a/2,0,appl_height hotspot a/2,0,appl_height hotspot a/2,-b,appl_height hotspot -a/2,-b,appl_height del 1
if iStyle = STYLE_PANEL then
add a/2,b,0
prism_ 9, 0.1, a/2, 0.0, 11, a/2, -b, 11, a/2-0.02, -b, 11, a/2-0.02, -b+0.01, 11, -a/2+0.02, -b+0.01, 11, -a/2+0.02, -b, 11, -a/2, -b, 11, -a/2, 0.0, 11, a/2, 0.0, -1
addz 0.1 prism_ 5, 0.25, a/2, 0.0, 10, a/2, -b, 10, -a/2, -b, 10, -a/2, 0.0, 10, a/2, 0.0, -1 lin_ -a/2 + 0.02,-b,0,a/2 - 0.02,-b,0 del 1
addz appl_height - 0.03 prism_ 5, 0.03, a/2, 0.0, 14, a/2, -b, 14, -a/2, -b, 14, -a/2, 0.0, 14, a/2, 0.0, -1
del 1
rotx 90 add 0,appl_height - 0.03,0
prism_ 5, b - 0.03, a/2, 0.0, 11, a/2, -appl_height + 0.38, 11, -a/2, -appl_height + 0.38, 11, -a/2, 0.0, 11, a/2, 0.0, -1
! --- door frame ---
addz b-0.03 resol 1.5 * gs_resol
prism_ 22, 0.03, a/2, 0.0, 14, a/2, -appl_height+0.38, 14, -a/2, -appl_height+0.38, 14, -a/2, 0.0, 14, a/2, 0.0, -1,
-a/2+0.09, -0.1, 15+64, -a/2+0.09, -0.14, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, -a/2+0.05, -0.14, 15+64, -a/2+0.05, -appl_height+0.47, 15+64, -a/2+0.09, -appl_height+0.47, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, -a/2+0.09, -appl_height+0.43, 15+64, a/2-0.09, -appl_height+0.43, 15+64, a/2-0.09, -appl_height+0.47, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, a/2-0.05, -appl_height+0.47, 15+64, a/2-0.05, -0.14, 15+64, a/2-0.09, -0.14, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, a/2-0.09, -0.1, 15+64, -a/2+0.09, -0.1, -1
! ---door ---
prism_ 17, 0.03, a/2-0.055, -0.14, 15+64, a/2-0.09, -0.14, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, a/2-0.09, -0.105, 15+64, -a/2+0.09, -0.105, 15+64, -a/2+0.09, -0.14, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, -a/2+0.055, -0.14, 15+64, -a/2+0.055, -appl_height+0.47, 15+64, -a/2+0.09, -appl_height+0.47, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, -a/2+0.09, -appl_height+0.435, 15+64, a/2-0.09, -appl_height+0.435, 15+64, a/2-0.09, -appl_height+0.47, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, a/2-0.055, -appl_height+0.47, 15+64, a/2-0.055, -0.14, -1 del 1 del 1 del 1
r = (a/2 - 0.01)**2 / 0.04 + 0.01
if bControlPanel = 1 then
add 0, 0, ZZYZX + 0.05 - storage_hgh rotx 65 cutplane del 2
add -a/2 + 0.35,0,ZZYZX - 1.1 - storage_hgh roty 75 cutplane del 2
rotx 90 resol 8 * gs_resol prism_ 6, 0.1, -a/2+0.01, appl_height, 15, -a/2+0.01, ZZYZX-0.02-storage_hgh, 15+64, 0.0, ZZYZX-r-storage_hgh, 915, a/2-0.01, ZZYZX-0.02-storage_hgh, 3015, a/2-0.01, appl_height, 15, -a/2+0.01, appl_height, -1 del 1
cutend
add a/2 - 0.35, 0, ZZYZX-1.1 - storage_hgh roty -75 cutplane del 2
rotx 90 prism_ 6, 0.1, -a/2+0.01, appl_height, 15, -a/2+0.01, ZZYZX-0.02-storage_hgh, 15+64, 0.0, ZZYZX-r-storage_hgh, 915, a/2-0.01, ZZYZX-0.02-storage_hgh, 3015, a/2-0.01, appl_height, 15, -a/2+0.01, appl_height, -1 del 1
cutend cutend
material k_mat
add 0, 0, ZZYZX + 0.05 - storage_hgh rotx 65 cutplane del 2
add -a/2 + 0.35, 0, ZZYZX - 1.1 - storage_hgh roty -105 cutplane del 2
add a/2 - 0.35, 0, ZZYZX - 1.1 - storage_hgh roty 105 cutplane del 2
rotx 90 prism_ 6,0.1, -a/2+0.01, appl_height, 15, -a/2+0.01, ZZYZX-0.02-storage_hgh, 15+64, 0.0, ZZYZX-r-storage_hgh, 915, a/2-0.01, ZZYZX-0.02-storage_hgh, 3015, a/2-0.01, appl_height, 15, -a/2+0.01, appl_height, -1 del 1
cutend cutend
cutend
endif !!!!! KNOB !!!!!
mul a/0.7,1,1 rotx 90 add 0,appl_height-0.03,b resol gs_resol material k_mat prism_ 8, 0.005, 0, 0.02, 15+64, 1, 0, 815+64, 0.3185, 0.0118, 1015+64, 0.3185, -0.0118, 1015+64, 0, -0.02, 1015+64, -0.3185, -0.0118, 1015+64, -0.3185, 0.0118, 1015+64, 0, 0.02, 1015+64 del 2 del 1
rotx 90 add 0, appl_height - 0.145,b prism_ 11, 0.005, -a/2+0.09, 0.0, 15+64, -a/2+0.09, -0.025, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, -a/2+0.065, -0.025, 15+64, -a/2+0.065, -0.035, 15+64, a/2-0.065, -0.035, 15+64, a/2-0.065, -0.025, 15+64, a/2-0.09, -0.025, 900, 0.0, 90.0, 4001, a/2-0.09, 0.0, 15, -a/2+0.09, 0.0, -1
del 4
else !------------------ Glazed front opening ---------------------
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DET3D_SIMPLE then gs_resol = 6 endif resol gs_resol
frontPanelHeight = appl_height - appl_height/30 - appl_height*12/90 - appl_height/90 r = min(a/3.5, frontPanelHeight/3.5, appl_height/5)
addy b*2/60 material w_mat rotx 90 prism_ 8, b*2/60, 0, 0, 15, a, 0, 15, a, frontPanelHeight, 15, 0, frontPanelHeight, 15, 0, 0, 13, 0, 0, -1, a/2, frontPanelHeight/2, 913, r, 360, 4013
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DET3D_SIMPLE then prism_ 2, 0.005, a/2, frontPanelHeight/2, 913, r, 360, 4013 endif
addz -b*2/60 material matDoorFrame if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DET3D_DETAILED then prism_ 3, b*2/60, a/2, frontPanelHeight/2, 979, r, 360, 4079, r-(r/5), 360, 4079 endif del 2
material matGlass add a/2, b*12/60, frontPanelHeight/2 roty -90 rotz -90 if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DET3D_DETAILED then revolve 2, 360, 1, 0, r-(r/2.5), 0, b*10/60, r-(r/5), 1 endif del 4
!--- box ---
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DET3D_SIMPLE then add 0, b*2/60, 0 prism_ 5, frontPanelHeight+appl_height*13/90, 0, 0, 15, a, 0, 15, a, b-0.02, 15, 0, b-0.02, 15, 0, 0, -1 del 1 else material w_mat
addy b*2/60 rotx 90 roty 90 for m=1 to 2 poly_ 5, 0, 0, 1, b - b * 2 / 60, 0, 1, b - b * 2 / 60, frontPanelHeight + appl_height * 13 / 90, 1, 0, frontPanelHeight + appl_height * 13 / 90, 1, 0, 0, -1 addz a next m del 5
addy b rotx 90 poly_ 5, 0, 0, 1, a, 0, 15, a, frontPanelHeight + appl_height * 13 / 90, 1, 0, frontPanelHeight + appl_height *13 / 90, 1, 0, 0, -1 del 1
rotx 180
poly_ 5, 0, 0, 1, a, 0, 15, a, b - b * 2 / 60, 1, 0, b - b * 2 / 60, 1, 0, 0, -1
del 2 endif
!--- control panel --- material matControlPanel add 0, b * 2 / 60, frontPanelHeight + appl_height / 90 rotx 90 prism_ 5, b * 2 / 60, 0, 0, 15, a, 0, 15, a, appl_height * 11 / 90, 15, 0, appl_height * 11 / 90, 15, 0, 0, -1
addy -appl_height / 90 poly_ 5, 0, 0, 1, a, 0, 1, a, appl_height * 13 / 90, 1, 0, appl_height * 13 / 90, 1, 0, 0, -1 del 3
!--- counter ---
material w_mat addz appl_height - (appl_height/30) prism_ 5, appl_height/30, 0, 0, 15, a, 0, 15, a, b, 15, 0, b, 15, 0, 0, -1 del 1
!--- knobs --- if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DET3D_DETAILED then material matControl add a/10, 0, appl_height - appl_height/30 - appl_height * 6/90 rotx 90 resol gs_resol for n=1 to 4 cylind b/60, a/60 addx a/15 next n del 6 endif
del 1 endif !!! ================ Laundry Storage ===========================
if gs_bLaundryStorage then call "fa_laundrystorage" parameters all endif
Symbol.Script_2D:
! --- Oriented View ------------------------------ [
angleViewRot = 0 if dt then rrr = REQUEST ("View_Rotangle", "", angleViewRot) endif totalRotate = (SYMB_ROTANGLE + angleViewRot) MOD 360
! --- Oriented View ------------------------------ ]
DrawingNum = 1 if DrawingNum = 1 then ! Top
unID = 1 pen gs_cont_pen
add2 a/2,b hotspot2 0, 0, unID: unID = unID + 1
fill gs_fill_type drawindex 20 poly2_b 5, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen,gs_back_pen, -a/2, 0, 1, -a/2, -b, 1, a/2, -b, 1, a/2, 0, 1, -a/2, 0, -1 del 1
! ========================================================================== ! Symbols ! ==========================================================================
if b2DSymbol and not(compatibilityForSymbolTypes = COMP_STATE_PLACEDorDEFAULT) then pen gs_symbol_pen aorb = a if a > b then aorb = b add2 a/2,b/2
if iDrierSymbolType = 1 then circle2 0,0,aorb/3.5 line2 -aorb/6,aorb/7,aorb/6,aorb/7 line2 0,aorb/7,0,-aorb/5 endif
if iDrierSymbolType = 2 then add2 0,b/5
rc=aorb/6 circle2 0, 0, rc line2 -0.25*rc, 0.96824*rc, -0.75*rc, -0.66143*rc line2 0.25*rc, 0.96824*rc, 0.75*rc, -0.66143*rc del 1 add2 0, -b/3 circle2 0, 0, aorb/15 fill gs_symbol_fill_type poly2_b 7, 1+2+64, gs_symbol_pen, gs_back_pen, aorb/15, 0, 1, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180, 4001, -aorb/15, 0, 1, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180, 4001, aorb/15, 0, 1 del 1 endif
if iDrierSymbolType = 3 then circle2 0,0,aorb/3.5 circle2 0,0,aorb/4.5 endif del 1 endif
drawindex 10 call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 20, unID = 3000
call "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
! ====================================================================== ! 2D TEXT ! ======================================================================
unID = 200 if dt then drawindex 30 nTrans = 0
hotspot2 a/2+txtx, b/2+txty, unID, txtx, 2 : unID = unID + 1 ! moving hotspot2 a/2, b/2+txty, unID, txtx, 1+128 : unID = unID + 1 ! base hotspot2 -1, b/2+txty, unID, txtx, 3 : unID = unID + 1 ! reference
hotspot2 a/2+txtx, b/2, unID, txty, 1+128 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 a/2+txtx, b/2+txty, unID, txty, 2 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 a/2+txtx, -1, unID, txty, 3 : unID = unID + 1
pen tpen define style textstyle fontType, fontSize * 1000 / GLOB_SCALE, 5, gs_text_style_bold + 2 * gs_text_style_italic + 4 * gs_text_style_underline style textstyle add2 a/2 + txtx, b/2 + txty nTrans = nTrans + 1
! Text Rotation - Readable / Always Horizontal / Align with Symbol ! ---------------------------------------------------------------------- if typeTextRotation_m = 2 then ! Readable rot2 180 * (totalRotate > (gs_readable_angle + eps) & totalRotate < (gs_readable_angle + 180 + eps)) ! 1/0 nTrans = nTrans + 1 else if typeTextRotation_m = 1 then ! Horizontal rot2 totalRotate * (SYMB_MIRRORED - not(SYMB_MIRRORED)) ! 1/-1 nTrans = nTrans + 1 endif endif ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------
text2 0,0,txt
del nTrans else hotspot2 a/2, b/2, unID endif endif del TOP
! --- start of modifying to Shaft
if bShowMEP then
pen gs_cont_pen
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
if DrawingNum = 2 then PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom if DrawingNum = 3 then PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front if DrawingNum = 4 then PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back if DrawingNum = 5 then PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right if DrawingNum = 6 then PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
call "MEP_m_ConnectionsACL_4" parameters SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 12
del 1 endif
! --- end of modifying to Shaft

! ============================================================================== ! Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
_autoID = "16D19E93-3037-42FA-8FA8-44D82DA7C1F7" _startID = "F365059F-D839-4099-9AC5-16E8469E7F76" _endID = "33ABB363-1C8F-435D-9AE0-46E0B73D5033" gosub "AddingGlazedStyle_FWM"
_startID = "33ABB363-1C8F-435D-9AE0-46E0B73D5033" _endID = "691D685B-D87E-4819-B687-DD797B6B96BE" gosub "FontSizeParamType_FWM"
! ============================================================================== ! Set migration GUID ! ==============================================================================
setmigrationguid actualGUID
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! en ! ==============================================================================
! ============================================================================== ! AddingGlazedStyle ! ============================================================================== "AddingGlazedStyle_FWM": if actualGuid = _startID | actualGuid = _autoID then
iStyle = STYLE_PANEL _ControlPanel = 0 bHas = DELETED_PAR_VALUE ("ControlPanel", _ControlPanel) bControlPanel = _ControlPanel
parameters bControlPanel = bControlPanel
! The drawing of the main body of the machine is different a little bit so when there is no controlpanel ! the zzyzx should decrease
if bControlPanel then appl_height = appl_height - 0.2 endif
parameters iStyle = iStyle, appl_height = appl_height
actualGuid = _endID endif return
! ============================================================================== ! Make the Font Size parameter a Length Type parameter ! ============================================================================== "FontSizeParamType_FWM": if actualGuid = _startID then bHas = DELETED_PAR_VALUE("fsz", _fsz)
fontSize = _fsz / 100 parameters fontSize = fontSize
actualGuid = _endID endif return
Symbol.Script_BWM:
targetGUID = TO_GUID
! ============================================================================== ! Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
gosub "FontSizeParamType_BWM"
gosub "AddingGlazedStyle_BWM"
! ============================================================================== ! Set migration GUID ! ==============================================================================
setmigrationguid targetGuid
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! en ! ==============================================================================
! ============================================================================== ! Make the Font Size parameter a Length Type parameter ! ============================================================================== "FontSizeParamType_BWM": if targetGUID # "" then newparameter "fsz", "RealNum" newparameter "fsz_point", "RealNum"
fsz = fontSize * 100 fsz_point = fontSize * 7200 / 25.4
parameters fsz = fsz, fsz_point = fsz_point endif return
! ============================================================================== ! AddingGlazedStyle ! ============================================================================== "AddingGlazedStyle_BWM": if targetGUID # "" then bMigrationSuccess = 1
if iStyle = STYLE_GLAZED then bMigrationSuccess = 0 else newparameter "ControlPanel", "Boolean"
ControlPanel = bControlPanel ZZYZX = appl_height + gs_LStorage_height * gs_bLaundryStorage + 0.2 * bControlPanel
parameters ControlPanel = ControlPanel, ZZYZX = ZZYZX
endif
if bMigrationSuccess = 0 then targetGuid = "" endif endif return
